# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-105">Защита от потери данных (DLP) в центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из следующих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-113">Номер маршрутизации код банка ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-113">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-114">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-114">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-115">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-115">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-116">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-116">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-117">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-117">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-118">четыре цифры, начинающиеся с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-118">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-119">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-119">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-120">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-120">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-121">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-121">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-122">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-122">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-123">Неформатированный: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-123">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-124">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-125">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-126">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-127">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-127">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-128">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-128">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-129">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-129">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- ABA Routing Number -->
<Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-143">американбанкассоЦиатионраутингнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-143">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-149">Внутренний идентификационный номер (DNI), Аргентина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-149">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-151">Восемь цифр, разделенных точками.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-151">Eight digits separated by periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-153">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-153">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-154">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-154">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-155">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-155">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-156">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-156">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-157">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-157">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-158">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-159">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-159">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-160">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-160">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-161">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-161">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-163">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-163">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-164">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-164">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-176">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-176">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-178">шесть – ТВН цифрами с номером филиала банка или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-178">six to twn digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-180">Номер счета — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-180">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-181">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-181">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-182">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-182">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-183">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-183">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-184">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-184">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-186">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-186">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-188">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-188">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-189">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-189">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-190">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-190">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-191">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-191">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-193">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-195">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-195">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-197">swift bank code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-197">swift bank code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-198">correspondent bank</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-198">correspondent bank</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-210">Бизнес-номер Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-210">Australia business number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-211">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-211">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-212">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-212">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-213">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-213">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-214">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-214">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-215">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-215">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-216">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-216">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-217">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-217">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-218">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-218">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-219">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-219">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-220">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-220">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-221">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-221">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-222">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-222">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-223">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-223">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-224">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-224">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-225">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-225">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-226">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-226">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-227">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-227">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-228">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-228">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-229">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-229">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-239">Номер компании Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-239">Australia company number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-240">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-240">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-241">девять цифр с разделителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-241">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-242">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-242">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-243">девять цифр с разделителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-243">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-244">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-244">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-245">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-245">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-246">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-246">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-247">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-247">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-248">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-248">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-249">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-249">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-250">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-250">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-251">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-251">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-252">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-252">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-253">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-253">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-254">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-254">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-255">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-255">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-256">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-256">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-266">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-266">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-267">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-268">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-268">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-269">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-270">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-270">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-271">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-271">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-272">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-272">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-273">пять цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-273">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-274">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-274">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-275">один-два необязательных буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-275">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-276">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-276">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-277">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-277">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-278">девять цифр или букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-278">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-279">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-279">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-280">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-280">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-281">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-281">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-282">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-282">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-283">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-283">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-284">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-284">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-285">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-285">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-305">Driver ' Licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-305">Driver'Licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-306">Driver ' Licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-306">Driver'Licences</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-385">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-385">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-386">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-386">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-387">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-387">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-388">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-388">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-389">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-389">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-390">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-390">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-391">девятая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-391">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-392">Десятая цифра — это цифра, связанная с вопросом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-392">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-393">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-393">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-394">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-395">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-395">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-396">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-397">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-397">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-398">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-398">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-399">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-399">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-400">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-400">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-403">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-403">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-404">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-404">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-405">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-405">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-406">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-406">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-407">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-407">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-408">credit card loan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-408">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-409">department of human services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-409">department of human services</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-412">Номер паспорта для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-412">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-413">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-413">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-414">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-414">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-415">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-415">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-416">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-416">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-417">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-417">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-418">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-418">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-419">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-419">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-420">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-420">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-421">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-421">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-422">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-422">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-423">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-423">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-424">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-424">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-425">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-425">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-426">Passport No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-426">Passport No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-427">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-427">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-428">Службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-428">Passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-429">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-429">PassportID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-430">пасспортно</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-430">Passportno</span></span>

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-456">Номер файла налога для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-456">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-457">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-457">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-458">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-458">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-459">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-459">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-460">от восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представляются пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-460">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-461">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-461">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-462">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-462">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-463">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-463">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-464">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-464">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-465">две и три цифры, где последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-465">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-466">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-466">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-467">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-467">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-468">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-468">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-469">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-469">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-470">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-470">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-471">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-471">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-472">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-472">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-484">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-484">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-485">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-485">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-486">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-486">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-487">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-487">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-488">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-488">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-489">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-489">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-490">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-490">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-491">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-491">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-492">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-492">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-493">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-493">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-494">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-494">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-495">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-495">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-512">Австрийская идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-512">Austria identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-513">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-514">24 – символическое сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-514">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-515">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-516">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-516">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="3def0-517">22 буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, косые черты и знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-517">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-518">две буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, знаки косой черты, знаки плюса и знаки равенства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-518">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-519">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-519">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-520">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-520">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-521">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-521">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-522">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-522">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-523">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-523">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-524">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-524">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-525">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-525">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-526">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-526">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-528">national id</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-530">Номер паспорта для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-530">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-531">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе сенситивеинформатион Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-531">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-532">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-532">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-533">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-533">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-534">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-534">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-535">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-535">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-536">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-536">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-537">один пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-537">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-538">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-538">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-539">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-539">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-540">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-540">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-541">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-541">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-542">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-542">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-543">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-543">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-544">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-544">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-545">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-545">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-546">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-546">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-547">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-547">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-548">Австрийский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-548">austrian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-549">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-549">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-550">реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-550">reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-551">öстерреичисч реисепасс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-551">österreichisch reisepass</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-552">Австрийский номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-552">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-553">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-553">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-554">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-554">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-555">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-555">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-556">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-556">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-557">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-557">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-558">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-558">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-559">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-559">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-560">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-560">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-561">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-562">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-562">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-563">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-564">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-564">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-565">Функция "Func_austria_eu_</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-565">The function  \`Func_austria_eu_</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-566">_or_equivalent ' находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-566">_or_equivalent\` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-567">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-567">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-568">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-568">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-569">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-569">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-583">созиале сичерхеит Кеин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-583">soziale sicherheit kein</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-584">версичерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-584">versicherungsnummer</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-585">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-585">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-586">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-587">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-587">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-588">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-589">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-589">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-590">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-590">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-591">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-591">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-592">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-592">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-593">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-593">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-594">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-594">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-595">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-595">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-596">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-596">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-597">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-597">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-598">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-598">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-599">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-599">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-600">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-600">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-601">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-601">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-602">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-602">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-625">Налог на добавленную стоимость (Австрия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-625">Austria value added tax</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-626">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-626">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-627">11-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-627">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-628">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-628">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-629">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-629">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-630">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-630">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-631">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-631">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-632">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-632">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-633">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-633">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-634">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-634">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-635">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-635">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-636">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-636">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-637">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-637">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-638">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-638">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-639">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-639">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-640">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-640">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-641">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-641">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-642">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-642">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-677">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-677">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-753">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-753">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-759">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-759">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->

        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-840">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-840">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-841">строка "SIG"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-841">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-842">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-842">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-843">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-843">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-844">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-844">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-845">любое сочетание 43-53 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-845">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-846">строка "% 3D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-846">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-847">любой символ, который не является буквой нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрой или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-847">any character that is not a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-848">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-848">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-849">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-849">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-850">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-850">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-851">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-851">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-852">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-852">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-868">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-868">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-904">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-904">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-908">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-908">No</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-910">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-910">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-932">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-932">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-933">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, знаков косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+) перед или за ними следуют символы, указанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-933">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-934">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-934">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-935">ноль к одному символу "больше" (>), апостроф ('), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или решетку (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-935">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-936">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые представляют собой буквы в нижнем или верхнем регистре, цифры, косую черту (/) или знак плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-936">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-937">два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-937">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-938">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-939">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-939">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-940">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-941">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-941">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-942">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-942">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-943">Номер водительского удостоверения для бельгийского драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-943">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-944">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-944">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-945">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-945">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-946">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-946">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-947">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-947">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-948">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-948">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-949">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-949">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-950">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-950">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-951">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-951">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-952">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-952">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-953">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-953">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-954">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-954">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-976">Бельгийский национальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-976">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-977">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-977">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-978">11 цифр, а также необязательные разделители</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-978">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-979">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-979">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-980">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-980">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-981">шесть цифр и две дополнительные точки в формате гг. Мм. DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-981">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-982">Необязательный разделитель из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-982">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-983">три последовательные цифры (нечетные для мужчин, даже для женщин).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-983">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-984">Необязательный разделитель из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-984">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-985">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-985">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-986">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-986">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-987">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-987">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-988">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-988">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-989">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-989">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-990">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-990">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-991">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-991">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-992">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-992">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-993">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-993">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-994">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-994">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-995">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-995">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
