## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1054">Номер паспорта Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1054">Belgium passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1055">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1055">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1056">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1056">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1057">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1057">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1058">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1058">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1059">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1059">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1060">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1061">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1061">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1062">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1063">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1063">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1064">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1064">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1065">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1065">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium__eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1068">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1068">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1069">Бельгийский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1069">belgian passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1071">паспурт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1071">paspoort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1072">паспуртнуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1072">paspoortnummer</span></span>

## <a name="belgium-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1075">Бельгийский номер социального страхования или идентификатор эквивалентной идентификации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1075">Belgium social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1076">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1076">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1077">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1078">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1078">11 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1079">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1080">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1080">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1081">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1081">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1082">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1082">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1083">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1083">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1084">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1084">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1085">Функция  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1085">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1086">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1086">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1087">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1087">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1088">Функция  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1088">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1108">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Бельгия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1108">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1109">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1109">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1110">12-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1110">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1111">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1111">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1112">12-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1112">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1113">буква B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1113">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1114">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1114">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1115">цифра 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1115">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1116">цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1116">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1117">Необязательная точка или дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1117">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1118">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1118">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1119">Необязательная точка или дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1119">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1120">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1120">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1121">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1121">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1122">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1122">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1123">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1123">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1124">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1124">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1125">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1125">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1126">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1126">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1127">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1127">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1128">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1128">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1129">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1129">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1130">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1130">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1131">n º тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1131">nº tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1132">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1132">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1133">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1133">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1134">нумéро t. v. a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1134">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1135">умсатзстеуер — идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1135">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1136">умсатзстеуернуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1136">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1137">бтв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1137">btw</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1138">бтв #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1138">btw#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1139">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1139">vat#</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1140">Номер CPF для Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1140">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1141">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1141">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1142">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1142">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1143">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1143">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1144">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1144">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1145">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1145">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1146">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1146">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1147">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1147">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1148">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1148">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1149">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1149">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1150">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1150">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1151">две цифры, которые проверяются</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1151">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1152">Неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1152">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1153">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1153">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1154">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1154">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1155">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1155">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1156">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1156">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1157">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1157">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1158">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1158">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1159">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1159">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1160">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1160">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1161">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1161">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1162">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1162">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1163">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1163">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1165">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1165">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1166">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1166">CPF</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1167">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1167">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1168">Registration</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1168">Registration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1169">Реализации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1169">Revenue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1170">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1170">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1171">импосто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1171">Imposto</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1172">идентификаçãо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1172">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1173">инскриçãо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1173">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1174">рецеита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1174">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1175">Номер юридического лица в Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1175">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1176">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1176">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1177">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1177">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1178">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1178">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1179">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1179">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1180">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1180">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1181">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1181">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1182">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1182">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1183">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1183">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1184">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр — регистрационный номер).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1184">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1185">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1185">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1186">номер филиала из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1186">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1187">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1187">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1188">две цифры, которые проверяются</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1188">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1189">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1189">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1190">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1190">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1191">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1191">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1192">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1193">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1193">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1194">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1195">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1195">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1196">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1196">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1197">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1197">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1198">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1198">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1209">Для бизнеса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1209">Business</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1210">Company</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1210">Company</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1211">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1211">CNPJ</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1220">Национальная идентификационная карточка Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1220">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1221">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1222">Registro Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1222">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1223">Registro de identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1223">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1224">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1224">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1225">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1225">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1226">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1226">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1227">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1227">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1228">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1228">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1229">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1229">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1230">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1230">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1231">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1231">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1232">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1232">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1233">Registro de identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1233">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1234">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1234">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1235">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1235">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1236">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1236">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1237">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1237">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1238">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1238">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1239">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1239">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1240">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1240">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1241">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1241">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1242">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1242">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1243">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1243">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1244">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1244">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1245">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1245">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1246">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1246">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
<Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1257">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1257">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1258">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1258">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1259">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1259">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1260">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1260">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1261">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1261">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1262">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1262">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1263">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1263">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1264">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1264">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1265">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1265">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1266">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1266">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1267">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1267">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1268">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1268">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
             <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern> 
</Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1287">Номер унифицированного гражданства Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1287">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1288">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1289">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1289">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1290">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1291">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1291">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1292">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1292">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1293">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1293">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1294">одна цифра, соответствующая Пол: четное число для пола и нечетная цифра для розетки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1294">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1295">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1295">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1296">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1296">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1297">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1297">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1298">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1298">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1299">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1299">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1300">Функция  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1300">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1301">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1301">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1302">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1302">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1303">Функция  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1303">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1346">униформгражданскиид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1346">униформгражданскиid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1347">униформгражданскине. #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1347">униформгражданскине.#</span></span>


## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1348">Номер паспорта для Болгария</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1348">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1349">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1349">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1350">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1350">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1351">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1351">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1352">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1352">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1353">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1353">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1354">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1354">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1355">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1355">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1356">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1356">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1357">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1357">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1358">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1358">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1359">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1359">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1360">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1360">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1361">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1361">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1362">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1362">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1363">номер паспорта для болгарского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1363">bulgarian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1364">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1364">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1365">номер на паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1365">номер на паспорта</span></span>


## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1366">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1366">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1367">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1368">семь или двенадцать цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1368">seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1369">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1370">Номер банковского счета для Канады — семь или двенадцать цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1370">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1371">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1371">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1372">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1372">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1373">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1373">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1374">три цифры или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1374">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1375">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1375">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1376">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1376">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1377">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1378">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1378">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1379">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1380">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1380">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1381">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1381">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1382">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1382">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1383">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1383">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1384">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1384">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1385">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1385">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1386">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1386">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1410">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1410">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1411">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1412">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1412">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1413">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1414">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1414">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1415">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1416">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1416">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1417">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1418">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1418">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1419">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1419">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1420">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1420">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1421">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1421">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1422">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1422">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_province_name_drivers_license_name"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1423">Keyword_ [province_name] _drivers_license_name</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1423">Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1424">Аббревиатура провинции, например AB.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1424">The province abbreviation, for example AB</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1425">Название провинции, например Альберта.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1425">The province name, for example Alberta</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_drivers_license"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1426">Keyword_canada_drivers_license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1426">Keyword_canada_drivers_license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1427">DL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1427">DL</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1428">БИБЛИОТЕК</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1428">DLS</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1429">кдл</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1429">CDL</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1430">кдлс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1430">CDLS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1432">дриверликс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1432">DriverLics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1433">дриверлиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1433">DriverLicense</span></span>

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1557">Номер службы здравоохранения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1557">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1558">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1558">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1559">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1559">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1560">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1560">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1561">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1561">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1562">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1562">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1563">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1563">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1564">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1564">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1565">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1565">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1566">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1566">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1567">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1567">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
```

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1579">Номер паспорта для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1579">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1580">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1581">две прописные буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1581">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1582">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1583">две прописные буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1583">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1585">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1585">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1587">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1587">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1588">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1588">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1589">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1589">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1619">Идентификационный номер персонального контроля работоспособности для Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1619">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1620">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1620">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1621">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1621">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1622">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1622">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1623">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1623">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1624">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1624">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1625">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1625">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1626">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1626">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1627">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1627">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1628">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1628">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1629">Найдены по крайней мере два ключевых слова от Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1629">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1662">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1662">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1663">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1663">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1664">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1664">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1665">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1665">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1666">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1666">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1667">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1667">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1668">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1668">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1669">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1669">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1670">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1670">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1671">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1671">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1672">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1672">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1673">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1673">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1674">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1674">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1675">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1675">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1676">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1676">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1677">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1677">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1678">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1678">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1679">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1679">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1680">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1680">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1681">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1681">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1682">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1682">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1683">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1683">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1684">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1684">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1685">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1685">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1686">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1686">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1711">Номер идентификационной карточки Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1711">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1712">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1712">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1713">семь и 8 цифр, а также разделители и контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1713">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1714">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1714">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1715">семь до восьми цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1715">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1716">одна – две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1716">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1717">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1717">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1718">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1718">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1719">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1719">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1720">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1720">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1721">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1721">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1722">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1722">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1723">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1724">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1724">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1725">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1726">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1727">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1727">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1728">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1728">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1729">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1729">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1730">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1730">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1731">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1731">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1732">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1732">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1745">Tarjeta de identificación</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1745">Tarjeta de identificación</span></span>

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1747">Номер почтовых карточек для Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1747">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1748">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1748">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1749">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1749">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1750">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1750">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1751">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1751">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1752">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1752">six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1753">восемь цифр в формате ГГГГММДД, представляющие собой дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1753">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1754">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1754">three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1755">одна цифра, представляющая собой контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1755">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1756">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1757">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1757">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-1758">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1759">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1759">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1760">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1760">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1761">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1761">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1762">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1762">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-1763">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1763">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1764">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1764">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-1765">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-1765">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
