## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2690">Эстонии персональный идентификационный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2690">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2691">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2691">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2692">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2692">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2693">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2693">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2694">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2694">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2695">одна цифра, соответствующая упоминанию секса и столетию рождения (нечетный номер, четная розетка), 1-2:19 века; 3-4:20 века; 5-6:21 столетие)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2695">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2696">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2696">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2697">три цифры, которые соответствуют порядковому номеру, разделенному на одну и ту же дату.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2697">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2698">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2698">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2699">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2699">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2700">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2700">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2701">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2701">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2702">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2702">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2703">Функция  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2703">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2704">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2704">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2705">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2705">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2706">Функция  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2706">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2723">tax id</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2739">Номер паспорта для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2739">Estonia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2740">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2740">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2741">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2742">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2742">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2743">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2744">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2744">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2745">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2746">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2746">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2747">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2748">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2748">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2749">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2749">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2750">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2750">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2757">Номер дебетовой карты ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2757">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2758">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2758">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2759">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2759">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2760">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2760">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2761">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2761">Very complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2762">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2763">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2763">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-2764">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2764">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-2765">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2765">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2766">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2766">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2767">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2767">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2768">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2768">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2769">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2769">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2770">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2770">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2771">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2771">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2772">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2772">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-2773">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-2773">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3219">Номер водительского удостоверения для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3219">Finland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3220">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3220">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3221">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3222">десять цифр, содержащие дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3222">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3223">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3223">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3224">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3224">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3225">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3225">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3226">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3226">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3227">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3227">four digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3229">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3229">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3231">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3231">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3232">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3232">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3233">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3233">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3234">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3234">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_finland_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3235">Keywords_finland_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3235">Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3236">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3236">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3237">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3237">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3238">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3238">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3239">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3239">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3240">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3240">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3241">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3241">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3242">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3242">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3243">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3243">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3244">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3244">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3245">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3245">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3246">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3246">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3247">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3247">dlno#</span></span>

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3249">Номер страховки для Финляндии (Европейский)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3249">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3250">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3250">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3251">20 цифр номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3251">20 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3252">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3252">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3253">20 – значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3253">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3254">десять цифр — 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3254">ten digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3255">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3255">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3256">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3256">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3257">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3257">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3258">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3258">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3259">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3259">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3260">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3260">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3261">Регулярное выражение Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3261">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3262">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3262">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3280">Национальный идентификатор Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3280">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3281">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3281">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3282">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на столетие плюс три цифры плюс контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3282">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3283">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3283">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3284">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3284">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3285">шесть цифр в формате формата ддммгг —, представляющие собой дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3285">six digits in the format format DDMMYY which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3286">маркер века ("-", "+" или "a")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3286">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3287">трехзначный идентификационный номер, соличный с тремя цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3287">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3288">цифра или буква (без учета регистра), которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3288">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3289">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3289">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3290">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3290">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3291">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3291">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3292">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3292">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3293">Функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3293">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3294">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_finnish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3294">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3295">Контрольная сумма проходит</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3295">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3296">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3296">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3297">Функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3297">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3298">Контрольная сумма проходит</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3298">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3347">Номер паспорта для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3347">Finland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3348">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3348">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3349">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3349">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3350">сочетание девяти букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3350">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3351">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3351">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3352">сочетание девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3352">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3353">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3353">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3354">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3354">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3355">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3355">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3356">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3356">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3357">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3357">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3358">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3358">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3359">регулярное выражение Regex_finland_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3359">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3360">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_finland_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3360">A keyword from Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3361">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3361">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3362">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3362">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3363">Службу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3363">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3364">пасси</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3364">Passi</span></span>


## <a name="finland-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3365">Номер социального страхования для Финляндии или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3365">Finland social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3366">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3366">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3367">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3368">11 символов в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3368">An 11-character combination in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3369">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3370">сочетание из 11 символов в указанном формате:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3370">an 11-character combination in the specified format:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3371">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3371">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3372">один из следующих экземпляров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3372">one instance of one of the following:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3373">символ "плюс"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3373">plus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3374">символ "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3374">minus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3375">буква "A" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3375">the letter "A" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3376">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3376">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3377">одна буква или одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3377">one letter or one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3378">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3378">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3379">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3379">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3380">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3380">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3381">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3381">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3382">Функция  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3382">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3383">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3383">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3384">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3384">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3385">Функция  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3385">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3395">код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3395">national id no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3396">Национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3396">national id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3397">ID No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3397">id no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3398">туннистенумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3398">tunnistenumero</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3401">аинутлаатуинен хенкилöкохтаинен туннус</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3401">ainutlaatuinen henkilökohtainen tunnus</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3409">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3409">France driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3410">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения для ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3410">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3411">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3412">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3412">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3413">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3414">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3414">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3415">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3416">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3416">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3417">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3418">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3418">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3419">Функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3419">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3420">выполняется по крайней мере одно из следующих условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3420">at least one of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3421">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3421">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3422">Функция Func_eu_date обнаружила дату в правильном формате даты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3422">the function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3423">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3423">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3425">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3425">drivers licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3427">driving licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3427">driving licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3428">driving license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3428">driving license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3429">permis de conduire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3429">permis de conduire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3430">licence number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3430">licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3431">license number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3431">license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3432">licence numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3432">licence numbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3433">license numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3433">license numbers</span></span>


## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3434">Номер страховки для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3434">France health insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3435">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3435">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3436">21 цифра цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3436">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3437">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3437">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3438">21 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3438">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3439">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3439">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3440">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3440">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3441">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3441">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3442">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3442">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3443">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3443">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3444">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3444">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3445">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3445">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3446">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3446">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3447">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3447">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3448">регулярное выражение Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3448">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3449">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3449">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3450">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3450">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3455">Национальный идентификационный номер страны Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3455">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3456">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3456">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3457">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3457">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3458">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3458">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3459">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3459">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3460">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3460">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3461">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3461">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3462">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3462">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3463">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3463">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3464">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3464">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3465">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3465">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3479">Номер паспорта для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3479">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3480">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3480">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3481">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3481">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3482">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3482">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3483">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3483">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3484">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3484">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3485">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3485">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3486">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3486">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3487">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3487">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3488">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3488">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3489">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3489">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3490">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3490">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3491">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3491">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3492">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3492">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3493">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3493">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3514">Номер социального страхования для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3514">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3515">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС и эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3515">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3516">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3516">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3517">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3517">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3518">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3518">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3519">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3519">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3520">13 цифр, за которыми следует пробел, за которым следуют две цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3520">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3521">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3521">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3522">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3522">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3523">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3523">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3524">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3524">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3525">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3525">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3526">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3526">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3527">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3527">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3528">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3528">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3529">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3529">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3530">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3530">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3531">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3531">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3532">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3532">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3533">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3533">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3547">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3547">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3548">д'идентите</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3548">d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3549">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3549">social security number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3552">le numéro d'identification nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3552">le numéro d'identification nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3553">d'identité nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3553">d'identité nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3554">numéro de sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3554">numéro de sécurité sociale</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3556">numéro d'assurance sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3556">numéro d'assurance sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3557">numéro de sécu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3557">numéro de sécu</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3559">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3559">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3560">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3560">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3561">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3561">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3562">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3562">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3563">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3563">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3564">Одна цифра, которая должна быть равна 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3564">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3565">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3565">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3566">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3566">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3567">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3567">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3568">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3568">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3569">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3569">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3570">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3570">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3571">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3571">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3572">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3572">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3573">3 контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3573">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3574">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3574">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3575">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3575">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3576">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3576">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3577">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3577">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3578">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3578">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3579">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3579">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3580">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3580">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3581">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3581">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3582">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3582">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3583">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3583">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3585">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3586">Налоговый идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3586">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3587">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3587">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3588">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3588">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3589">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3589">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3590">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3590">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3591">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3591">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3592">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3592">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3593">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3593">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3594">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3594">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3595">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3595">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3596">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3596">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3597">такснумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3597">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3598">Идентификатор Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3598">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3599">номер Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3599">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3600">ИНН #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3600">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3601">Значение налогового номера, добавленного в Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3601">France value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3602">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3602">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3603">13-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3603">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3604">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3604">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3605">13 символов буквенно-цифрового шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3605">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3606">две буквы — FR (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3606">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3607">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3607">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3608">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3608">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3609">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3609">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3610">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3610">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3611">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3611">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3612">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3612">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3613">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3613">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3614">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3614">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3615">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3616">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3616">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3617">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3618">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3618">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3619">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3619">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3620">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3620">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3621">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3621">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3622">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3622">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3623">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3623">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3624">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3624">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3625">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3625">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3626">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3626">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3627">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3627">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3628">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3628">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3629">Siren идентификация No нумéро д'идентификатион таксе Сур валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3629">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3630">таксе валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3630">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3631">таксе Сур Ла валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3631">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3632">n ° тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3632">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3633">нумéро de тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3633">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3634">нумéро д'идентификатион Siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3634">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3635">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3635">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3636">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3636">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3637">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3637">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3638">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3638">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3639">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3639">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3640">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3640">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3641">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3641">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3642">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3642">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3643">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3643">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3644">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3644">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3645">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3645">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3647">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3647">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3649">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3649">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3650">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3650">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3651">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3651">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3652">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3652">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3653">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3653">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3654">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3654">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml

<Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />

          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license_number" />
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3748">Номер идентификационной карточки для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3748">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3749">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3749">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3750">с 1 ноября 2010: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3750">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3751">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3751">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3752">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3752">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3753">с 1 ноября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3753">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3754">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3754">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3755">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3755">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3756">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3756">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3757">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3757">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3758">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3758">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3759">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3759">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3760">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3760">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3761">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3761">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3762">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3762">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3763">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3763">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3764">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3764">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3765">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3765">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3766">аусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3766">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3767">гпид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3767">gpid</span></span>
