## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3779">Номер паспорта для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3779">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3780">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3780">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3781">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3781">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3782">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3782">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3783">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3783">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3784">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3784">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3785">Первый символ — цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3785">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3786">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3786">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3787">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C,-H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3787">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3788">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3788">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3789">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3789">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3790">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3790">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3791">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3791">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3792">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3792">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3793">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3793">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3794">находится любое ключевое слово из пяти соответствующих списков;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3794">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3795">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3795">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3796">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3796">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3797">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3797">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3798">находится любое ключевое слово из пяти соответствующих списков;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3798">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3799">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3799">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Passport Number -->
<Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3817">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Германия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3817">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3818">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3818">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3819">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3819">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3820">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3820">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3821">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3821">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3822">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3822">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3823">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3823">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3824">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3824">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3825">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3825">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3826">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3826">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3827">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3827">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3828">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3828">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3829">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3829">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3830">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3830">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3831">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3831">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3832">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3832">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3833">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3833">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3834">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3834">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3835">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3835">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3836">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3836">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3837">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3837">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3854">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3854">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3855">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3855">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3856">такснумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3856">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3857">Идентификатор Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3857">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3858">номер Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3858">tin no</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3863">Значение налогового номера добавленного в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3863">Germany value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3865">11 буквенно-цифрового шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3865">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3867">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3867">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3868">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3868">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3869">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3869">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3870">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3870">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3871">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3871">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3872">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3872">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3873">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3873">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3874">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3874">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3875">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3875">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3876">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3876">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3877">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3877">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3878">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3878">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3879">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3879">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3880">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3880">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3881">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3881">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3882">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3882">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3883">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3883">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3884">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3884">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3885">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3885">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3886">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3886">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3887">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3887">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3888">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3888">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3889">НДС # мехрвертстеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3889">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3890">мвст</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3890">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3891">мехрвертстеуер идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3891">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3892">мехрвертстеуер нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3892">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3893">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3893">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3894">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3894">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3895">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3896">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3896">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3898">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3898">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3899">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3899">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3900">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3900">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3901">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3901">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3902">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3902">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3903">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3903">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3904">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3904">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3905">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3905">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3906">Keywords_greece_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3906">Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3909">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3909">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3910">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3910">driver licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3912">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3912">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3913">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3913">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3914">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3914">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3915">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3915">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3916">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3916">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3917">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3917">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3918">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3918">dlno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3919">δεια οδήγησης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3919">δεια οδήγησης</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3920">Адеиа одигисис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3920">Adeia odigisis</span></span>


## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3921">Национальный идентификационный номер карты (Греция)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3921">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3922">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3922">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3923">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3923">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3924">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3924">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3925">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3925">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3926">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3926">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3927">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3927">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3928">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3928">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3929">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3929">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3930">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3930">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3931">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3931">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3932">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3932">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3933">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3933">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3934">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3934">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3935">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3935">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3936">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3936">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3937">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3937">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3938">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3938">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3939">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3939">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3940">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3940">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3941">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3941">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3942">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3942">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3943">Греческий идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3943">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3944">Греческая национальная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3944">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3945">Греческая личная идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3945">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3946">код греческой политики</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3946">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3947">идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3947">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3948">таутотита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3948">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3949">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3949">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3950">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3950">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3951">Номер паспорта для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3951">Greece passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3952">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3952">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3953">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3953">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3954">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3954">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3955">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3955">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3956">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3956">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3957">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3957">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3958">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3958">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3959">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3959">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3960">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3960">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3961">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3961">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3962">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3962">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3969">Идентификационный номер налога в Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3969">Greece tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3970">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3971">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3971">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3972">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3973">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3973">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3974">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3974">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3975">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3975">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-3976">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3976">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-3977">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3977">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3978">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3978">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-3979">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-3979">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4008">Номер идентификационной карточки Гонконг (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4008">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4009">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4009">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4010">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4010">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4011">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4011">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4012">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4012">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4013">1–2 буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4013">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4014">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4014">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4015">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4015">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4016">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4016">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4017">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4017">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4018">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4018">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4019">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4019">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4020">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4020">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4021">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4021">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4022">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4022">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4023">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4023">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4024">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4024">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4025">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4025">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4065">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4065">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4066">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4066">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4067">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4067">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4068">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4068">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4069">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4069">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4070">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4070">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4071">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4071">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4072">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4072">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4073">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4073">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4074">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4074">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4075">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4075">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4076">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4076">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4077">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4077">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4078">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4078">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4094">Венгрия персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4094">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4095">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4096">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4096">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4097">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4097">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4098">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4098">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4099">Одна цифра, соответствующая пол (1-м-штекер, 2-гнездо, другие номера также могут иметь гражданские телефоны перед 1900 или гражданами с удвоенной гражданией)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4099">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4100">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4100">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4101">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4101">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4102">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4102">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4103">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4104">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4104">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4105">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4106">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4106">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4107">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4107">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4108">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4108">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4109">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4109">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4110">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4110">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4114">identification number
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4114">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4115">СЗ IG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4115">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4116">СЗ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4116">sz.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4117">IG.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4117"> ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4118">СЗ. IG.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4118">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4119">сземéлязоносíтó игазолвáни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4119">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4120">сземéли игазолвáни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4120">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4121">Номер паспорта для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4121">Hungary passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4122">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4122">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4123">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4123">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4124">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4124">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4125">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4125">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4126">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4126">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4127">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4127">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4128">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4128">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4129">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4129">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4130">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4131">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4131">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4132">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4132">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4133">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4133">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4134">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4134">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4135">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4135">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4136">Венгерский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4136">hungarian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4137">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4137">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4138">úтлевéл сзáма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4138">útlevél száma</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4139">Венгерский номер социального страхования или идентификация эквивалентных прав</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4139">Hungary social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4140">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4140">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4141">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4141">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4142">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4142">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4143">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4143">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4144">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4144">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4145">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4145">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4146">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4146">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4147">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4147">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4148">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4148">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4149">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4149">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4150">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4150">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4151">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4151">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4152">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4152">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4172">Идентификационный номер венгерского налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4172">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4173">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4173">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4174">Десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4174">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4175">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4175">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4176">Десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4176">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4177">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4177">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4178">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4178">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4179">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4179">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4180">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4181">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4181">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4182">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4183">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4183">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4184">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4184">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4185">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4185">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4186">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4186">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4187">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4187">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4213">Венгерский номер добавленного значения налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4213">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4214">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4214">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4215">10-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4215">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4216">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4216">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4217">10 буквенно-цифровых буквенных символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4217">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4218">2 буквы — HU или HU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4218">2 letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4219">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4219">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4220">8 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4220">8 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4221">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4221">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4222">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4222">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4223">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4223">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4224">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4224">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4225">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4225">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4226">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4226">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4227">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4227">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4228">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4228">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4231">процент</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4231">vat</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4239">áлталáнос форгалми адó сзáм</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4239">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4240">хоззáадоттéртéк адó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4240">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4241">áфа сзáм</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4241">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4242">Номер постоянного счета Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4242">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4243">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4243">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4244">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4244">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4245">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4245">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4246">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4246">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4247">пять букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4247">Five letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4248">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4248">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4249">буква, которая является алфавитным проверочным символом.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4249">A letter which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4250">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4250">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4251">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4251">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4252">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4252">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4253">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4253">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4254">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4254">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4255">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4255">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4256">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4256">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
<Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4261">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4261">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4262">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4262">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4263">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4263">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4264">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4264">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4265">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4265">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4266">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4266">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4267">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4267">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4268">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4268">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4269">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4269">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4270">последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4270">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4271">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4271">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4272">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4272">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4273">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4273">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4274">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4274">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4275">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4275">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4276">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4276">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4277">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4277">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4278">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4278">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4279">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4279">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4280">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4280">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4281">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4281">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4282">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4282">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4283">аадхар</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4283">Aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4284">Aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4284">Aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4285">UID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4285">UID</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4287">Номер идентификационной карточки Индонезия (KTP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4287">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4288">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4289">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4289">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4290">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4291">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4291">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4292">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4292">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4293">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4293">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4294">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4294">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4295">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4295">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4296">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4296">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4297">шесть цифр в формате ДДММГГ (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4297">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4298">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4298">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4299">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4299">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4300">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4300">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4301">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4301">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4302">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4302">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4303">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4303">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4304">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4304">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4305">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4305">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4306">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4306">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4307">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4307">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>
