## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4311">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4311">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4312">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4313">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4313">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4314">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4314">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4315">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4315">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4316">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4316">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4317">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4317">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4318">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4318">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4319">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4319">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-p131">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-p131">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4322">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4322">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4323">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4323">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4324">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4324">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4325">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4325">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4326">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4326">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4327">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4327">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4328">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4328">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4329">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4329">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4330">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4330">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4331">Международная классификация Diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4331">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4332">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4332">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4333">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4333">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4334">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4334">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4335">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4335">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4336">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4336">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4337">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4337">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4338">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4338">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4339">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4339">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4340">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4340">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4341">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4341">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4342">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4342">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4343">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_ "Обновлено".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4343">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4344">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4344">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4345">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_updated ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, десятой версии, Клиникал модификации (ICD-10-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4345">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4346">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4346">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4349">Международная классификация Diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4349">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4350">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4350">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4351">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4351">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4352">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4352">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4353">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4353">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4354">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4354">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4355">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4355">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4356">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4356">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4357">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4357">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4358">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4358">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4359">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4359">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4360">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4360">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4361">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4361">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4362">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4362">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4363">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, девятой редакции, Клиникал модификации (ICD-9-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4363">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4364">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4364">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4365">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, девятой редакции, Клиникал модификации (ICD-9-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4365">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4366">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4366">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4367">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4367">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4368">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4368">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4369">IPv4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4369">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4370">Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные (с точками) и неформатированные (без точек) версии IPv4-адресов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4370">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4371">Поддерживающ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4371">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4372"> Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные номера IPv6 (вместе с двоеточиями).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4372">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4373">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4373">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4374">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4374">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4375">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4375">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4376">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4376">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4377">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4377">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4378">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4378">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4379">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4379">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4380">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4380">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4381">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4381">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4382">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4382">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4383">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4383">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4384">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4384">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4385">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4385">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4393">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4393">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4394">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4394">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4395">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4395">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4396">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4396">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4397">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4397">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4398">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4398">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4399">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4399">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4400">Четыре буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4400">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4401">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4401">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4402">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4402">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4403">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4403">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4404">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4404">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4405">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4405">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4406">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4406">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4422">Номер паспорта для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4422">Ireland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4423">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4423">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4424">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4425">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4425">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4426">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4426">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4427">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4427">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4428">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4428">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4429">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4429">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4430">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4430">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4431">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4431">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4432">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4432">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4433">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4433">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4434">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4434">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4435">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4435">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4445">Номер личной общедоступной службы (PPS) Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4445">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4446">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4446">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4447">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4447">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4448">семь цифр, за которыми следует 1-2 букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4448">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4449">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4449">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4450">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4450">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4451">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4451">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4452">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4452">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4453">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4453">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4454">одна-2 буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4454">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4455">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4455">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4456">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4456">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4457">буква (без учета регистра), которая является буквенной контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4457">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4458">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A – I или "W"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4458">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4460">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4460">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4462">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4462">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4463">Функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4463">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4464">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4464">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4465">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4465">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4466">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4466">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4467">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4467">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4468">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4468">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4513">Номер банковского счета для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4513">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4514">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4514">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4515">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4515">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4516">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4516">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4517">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4517">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4518">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4518">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4519">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4519">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4520">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4520">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4521">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4521">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4522">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4522">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4523">Неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4523">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4524">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4524">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4525">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4525">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4526">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4526">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4527">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4527">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4528">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4528">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4529">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4529">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4530">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4530">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4531">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4531">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4532">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4532">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4533">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4533">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4534">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4534">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4535">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4535">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4536">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4536">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4537">Национальный идентификационный номер Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4537">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4539">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4539">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4541">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4541">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4542">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4542">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4543">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4543">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4544">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4544">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4545">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4545">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4546">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4546">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4547">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4547">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4548">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4548">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4549">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4549">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4550">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4550">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4551">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4551">מספר זהות</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4552">National ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4552">National ID Number</span></span>
   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4553">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4553">Italy driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4554">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4554">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4555">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4555">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4556">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4556">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4557">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4557">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4558">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4558">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4559">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4559">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4560">буква "A" или "V" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4560">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4561">семь букв (без учета регистра), цифр или символ подчеркивания.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4561">seven letters (not case sensitive), digits, or the underscore character</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4562">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4562">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4563">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4563">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4564">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4564">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4565">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4565">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4566">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4566">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4567">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4567">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4568">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4568">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4569">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4569">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4570">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4570">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4571">numero di patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4571">numero di patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4572">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4572">patente di guida</span></span> 

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4573">Финансовый код Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4573">Italy fiscal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4574">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4574">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4575">16 – символическое сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4575">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4576">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4576">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4577">16 – буквенное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4577">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4578">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем согласным в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4578">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4579">три буквы, соответствующие первым, третьим и четвертым согласным в имени.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4579">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4580">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4580">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4581">одна буква, соответствующая букве дня рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы от A до E, H, L, M, P, R — T (то есть Январь — это R, а Октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4581">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4582">две цифры, которые соответствуют дню месяца рождения, для различения пола, 40 добавляется в день рождения для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4582">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4583">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду города, который относится к органу государственной власти, в котором был создан пользователь, (для иностранных стран используются коды уровня страны).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4583">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4584">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4584">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4585">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4585">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4586">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4586">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4587">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4587">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4588">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4588">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4589">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4589">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4590">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4590">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4591">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4591">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4592">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4592">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4594">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4594">Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4604">личный номер сертификата</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4604">personal certificate number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4606">личный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4606">personal id code</span></span>

</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4610">tax id</span></span>

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4627">Номер паспорта для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4627">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4628">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4628">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4629">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4629">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4630">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4630">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4631">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4631">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4632">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4632">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4633">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4633">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4634">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4634">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4635">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4635">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4636">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4636">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4637">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4637">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4638">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4638">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4639">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4639">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4640">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4640">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4652">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Италия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4652">Italy value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4653">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4653">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4654">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенный шаблон с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4654">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4655">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4655">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4656">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-цифровой шаблон с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4656">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4657">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4657">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4658">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4658">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4659">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4659">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4660">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4660">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4661">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4661">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4662">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4662">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4663">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4663">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4664">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4664">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4665">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4665">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4666">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4666">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4667">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4667">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4668">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4668">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4670">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4670">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4676">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4676">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4677">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4677">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4678">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4678">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4679">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4679">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4680">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4680">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4681">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4681">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4682">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4682">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4683">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4683">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4684">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4684">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4685">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4685">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4686">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4686">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4687">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4687">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4688">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4688">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4689">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4689">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4690">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4690">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4691">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4691">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4692">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4692">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4693">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4693">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4694">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4694">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4695">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4695">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4696">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4696">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4697">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4697">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4756">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4756">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4757">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4757">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4758">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4758">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4759">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4759">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4760">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4760">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4762">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4762">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4764">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4764">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4765">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4765">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4766">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4766">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4794">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4794">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4795">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4795">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4796">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4796">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4797">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4797">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4798">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4798">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4799">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4799">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4800">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4800">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4801">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4802">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4802">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4803">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4804">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4804">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4805">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4805">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4806">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4806">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4807">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4807">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4808">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4808">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4821">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4821">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4822">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4822">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4823">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4823">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4824">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4824">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4825">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4825">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4826">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4826">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4827">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4827">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4828">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4828">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4829">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4829">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4830">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4830">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4831">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4831">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4832">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4832">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4833">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4833">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4834">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4834">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4835">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4835">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4836">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4836">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4837">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4837">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4838">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4838">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
```

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4851">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4851">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4852">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4852">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4853">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4853">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4854">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4854">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4855">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4855">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4856">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4856">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4857">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4857">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4858">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4858">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4859">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4859">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4860">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4860">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4861">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4861">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4868">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4868">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4869">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4869">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4870">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4870">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4871">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4871">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4872">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4872">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4873">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4873">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4874">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4874">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4875">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4875">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4876">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4876">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4877">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4877">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4878">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4878">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4879">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4879">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4880">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4880">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4881">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4881">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4893">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4893">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4896">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4896">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
```
