## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4912">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4912">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4913">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4913">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4914">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4914">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4915">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4915">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4916">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4916">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4917">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4917">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4918">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4918">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4919">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4919">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4920">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4920">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4921">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4921">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4922">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4922">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4923">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4923">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4924">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4924">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4925">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4925">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4926">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4926">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4927">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4927">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4928">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4928">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4929">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4929">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4936">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4936">社会保険番号</span></span> 

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4937">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4937">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4938">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4938">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4939">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4939">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4940">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4940">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4941">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4941">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4942">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4942">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4943">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4943">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4944">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4944">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4945">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4945">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4946">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4946">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4947">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4947">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4948">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4948">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4949">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4949">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4950">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4950">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4966">Личный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4966">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4967">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4967">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4968">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4968">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4969">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4969">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4970">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4970">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4971">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4971">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4972">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4972">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4973">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4973">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4974">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4974">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4975">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4975">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4976">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4976">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4977">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4977">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4978">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4978">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4979">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4979">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4980">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4981">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4981">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-4982">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4983">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4983">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4984">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4984">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4985">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4985">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-4986">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4986">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-4987">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-4987">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5050">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5050">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5051">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5051">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5052">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5052">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5053">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5053">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5054">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5054">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5055">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5055">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5056">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5056">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5057">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5057">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5058">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5058">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5059">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5059">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5060">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5060">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5061">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5061">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5062">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5062">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5063">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5063">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5064">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5064">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5065">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5065">Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5066">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5066">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5067">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5067">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5068">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5068">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5069">ПАСЕ нумурс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5069">pase numurs</span></span>    


## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5070">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5070">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5071">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5071">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5072">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5072">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5073">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5073">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5074">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5074">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5075">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5075">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5076">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5076">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5077">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5077">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5078">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5078">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5079">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5079">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5080">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5080">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5081">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5081">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5097">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5097">Lithuania personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5098">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5098">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5099">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5099">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5100">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5100">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5101">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5101">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5102">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5102">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5103">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5103">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5104">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5104">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5105">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5105">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5106">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5107">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5107">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5108">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5109">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5109">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5110">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5110">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5111">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5111">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5112">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5112">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5113">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5113">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5126">пилиеčио паслаугос нумерис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5126">piliečio paslaugos numeris</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5129">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5129">tax identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5132">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5132">tax number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5135">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5135">taxidno#</span></span>

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5148">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5148">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5149">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5149">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5151">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5151">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5153">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5153">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5154">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5154">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5155">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5155">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5156">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5156">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5157">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5157">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5158">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5158">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5159">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5159">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5160">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5160">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5161">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5161">Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5162">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5162">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5164">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5164">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5166">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5166">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5167">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5167">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5168">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5168">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5169">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5169">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5170">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5170">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5171">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5171">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5172">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5173">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5173">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5174">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5175">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5175">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5176">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5176">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5177">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5177">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5193">Национальный идентификационный номер Луксембург (для природных людей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5193">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5194">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5194">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5195">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5195">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5196">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5196">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5197">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5197">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5198">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5198">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5199">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5199">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5200">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5201">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5201">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5202">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5203">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5203">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5204">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5204">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5205">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5205">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5206">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5206">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5207">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5207">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5230">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5230">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5231">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5231">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5232">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5232">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5233">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5233">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5234">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5234">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5235">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5235">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5236">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5237">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5237">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5238">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5239">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5239">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5240">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5240">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5241">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5241">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5248">Луксембург Национальный идентификационный номер (неестественные пользователи)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5248">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5249">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5249">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5250">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5250">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5251">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5251">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5252">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5252">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5253">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5253">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5254">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5254">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5255">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5255">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5256">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5256">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5257">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5257">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5258">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5258">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5259">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5259">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5260">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5260">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5261">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5262">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5262">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5263">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5264">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5264">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5265">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5265">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5266">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5266">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5267">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5267">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5268">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5268">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5308">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5308">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5309">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5309">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5310">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5310">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5311">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5311">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5312">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5312">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5313">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5313">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5314">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5314">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5315">код места рождения из двух букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5315">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5316">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5316">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5317">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5317">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5318">код пола из одной цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5318">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5319">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5319">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5320">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5320">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5321">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5321">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5322">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5322">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5323">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5323">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5324">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5324">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5325">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5325">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_malaysia_id_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5326">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5326">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5340">ключев</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5340">kp</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5351">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5351">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5352">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5352">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5353">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5354">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5354">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5355">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5356">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5356">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5357">два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5357">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5358">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5358">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5359">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5359">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5360">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5360">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5361">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5361">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5362">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5362">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5363">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5363">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5364">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5364">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5365">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5365">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5366">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5366">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5367">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5367">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
 <Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5370">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5370">dl#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5372">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5372">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5373">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5373">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5374">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5374">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5375">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5375">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5376">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5376">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5377">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5377">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5378">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5378">driver's license number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5380">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5380">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5383">Номер идентификационной карточки Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5383">Malta identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5384">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5384">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5385">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5385">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5386">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5386">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5387">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5387">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5388">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5388">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5389">одна буква в письмах "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5389">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5390">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5390">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5391">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5391">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5392">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5392">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5393">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5393">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5394">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5394">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5395">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5395">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5396">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5396">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5397">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5397">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5404">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5404">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5405">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони ТАТ такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5405">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5406">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5406">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5407">нумру Ta ' идентитà унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5407">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5408">нумруные зада сервизз таċ ċиттадин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5408">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5409">нумру ТАТ — такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5409">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5410">персональный числовой код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5410">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5411">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5411">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5412">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5412">unique identity number</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5414">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5414">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5415">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5415">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5416">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5416">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5417">семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5417">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5418">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5418">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5419">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5419">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5420">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5420">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5421">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5421">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5422">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5422">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5423">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5423">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5424">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5424">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5425">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5425">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5426">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5426">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5427">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5427">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5428">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5428">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5430">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5430">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5432">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5432">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5433">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5433">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5434">Для национальных Мальтийский:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5434">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5435">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5435">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5436">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5436">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5437">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5437">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5438">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5438">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5439">Мальтийский Nationals: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5439">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5440">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5440">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5441">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5441">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5442">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не связанные с организациями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5442">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5443">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5443">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5444">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5444">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5445">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5445">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5446">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5446">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5447">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5447">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5448">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5448">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5449">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5449">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5450">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5450">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5451">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5451">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5484">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5484">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5485">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5485">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5486">восемь девяти цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5486">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5487">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5487">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5488">восемь девяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5488">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5489">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5489">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5490">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5490">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5491">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5491">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5492">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5492">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5493">две три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5493">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5494">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5495">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5495">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5496">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5497">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5497">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5498">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5498">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5499">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5499">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5500">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5500">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5503">BSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5503">bsn#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5506">номер службы для себя</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5506">citizen service number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5507">номер пользователя</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5507">person number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5509">персональный числовой код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5509">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5510">номер, связанный с человеком</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5510">person-related number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5511">персунлижк нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5511">persoonlijk nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5512">персунлижке нумериеке код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5512">persoonlijke numerieke code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5513">персунсжебонден</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5513">persoonsgebonden</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5514">персунснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5514">persoonsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5515">соЦиаал — фискаал нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5515">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5516">социальное — финансовый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5516">social-fiscal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5517">софи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5517">sofi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5518">софинуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5518">sofinummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5519">униек идентификатиенуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5519">uniek identificatienummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5520">униек идентитеитснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5520">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5521">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5521">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5522">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5522">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5523">уникуеидентитино #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5523">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5524">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5524">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5525">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5525">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5526">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5526">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5527">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5527">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5528">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5528">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5529">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5529">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5530">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5530">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5531">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5531">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5532">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5532">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5533">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5533">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5534">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5534">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5535">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5535">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
