## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5553">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5553">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5554">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5554">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5555">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5555">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5556">девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5556">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5557">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5557">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5558">девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5558">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5559">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5559">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5560">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5560">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5561">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5561">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5562">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5562">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5563">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5563">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5564">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5564">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5574">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5574">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5575">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5576">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5576">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5577">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5578">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5578">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5579">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5580">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5580">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5581">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5582">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5582">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5583">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5583">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5584">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5584">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5585">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5585">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5586">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5586">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5624">Номер налога добавленных значений в Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5624">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5625">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5625">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5626">14-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5626">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5627">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5627">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5628">14-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5628">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5629">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5629">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5630">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5630">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5631">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5631">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5632">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5632">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5633">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5633">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5634">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5634">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5635">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5635">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5636">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5636">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5637">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5637">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5638">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5638">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5639">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5639">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5640">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5640">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5641">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5641">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5642">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5642">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5643">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5643">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5652">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5652">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5653">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5653">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5654">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5654">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5655">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5655">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5656">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5656">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5657">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5657">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5658">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5658">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5659">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5659">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5660">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5660">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5661">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5661">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5662">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5662">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5663">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5663">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5664">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5664">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5665">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5665">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5666">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5666">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5667">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5667">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5668">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5668">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5669">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5669">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5670">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5670">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5671">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5671">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5672">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5672">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5680">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5680">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5681">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5681">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5682">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5682">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5683">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5683">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5684">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5684">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5685">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5685">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5686">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5686">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5687">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5687">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5688">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5688">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5689">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5689">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5690">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5690">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5691">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5691">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5692">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5692">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5693">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5693">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5694">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5694">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5761">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5761">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5762">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5763">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5763">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5764">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5765">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5765">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5766">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5766">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5767">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5767">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5768">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5768">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5769">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5769">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5770">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5770">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5771">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5771">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5772">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5772">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5773">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5773">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5774">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5774">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5775">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5775">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5776">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5776">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5777">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5777">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5778">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5778">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5779">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5779">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5780">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5780">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5781">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5781">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5782">ИРД нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5782">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5783">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5783">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5784">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5784">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5785">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5785">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5786">номер дохода на землю</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5786">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5787">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5787">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5788">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5788">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5789">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5789">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5790">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5790">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5791">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5791">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5792">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5792">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5793">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5793">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5794">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5794">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5795">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5795">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5796">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5796">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5797">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5797">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5798">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5798">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5799">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5799">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5800">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5800">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5801">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5801">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5802">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5802">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5803">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5803">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5804">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5804">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5805">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5805">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5806">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5807">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5807">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5808">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5809">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5809">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5810">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5810">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5811">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5811">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5812">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5812">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5813">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5813">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5814">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5814">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5815">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5815">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5816">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5816">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5817">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5817">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5818">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5818">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5819">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5819">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5820">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5820">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5821">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5821">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5822">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5822">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5823">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5823">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5824">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5824">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5825">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5825">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5826">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5826">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5827">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5827">social welfare No.</span></span>

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5830">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5830">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5831">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5831">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5832">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5832">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5833">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5833">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5834">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5834">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5835">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5835">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5836">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5836">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5837">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5837">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5838">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5838">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5839">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5839">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5840">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5840">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5841">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5841">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5842">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5842">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5843">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5843">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5844">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5844">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5845">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5845">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5846">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5846">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5847">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5847">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5856">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5856">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5857">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5857">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5858">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5858">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5859">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5859">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5860">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5860">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5861">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5861">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5862">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5862">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5863">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5863">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5864">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5864">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5865">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5865">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5866">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5866">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5867">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5867">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5868">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5868">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5869">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5869">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5870">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5870">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5871">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5871">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5872">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5872">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5873">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5873">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5874">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5874">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5875">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5875">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5876">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5876">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5877">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5877">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5878">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5878">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5879">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5879">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5880">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5880">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5881">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5881">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5882">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5882">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5883">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5883">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5884">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5884">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5885">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5885">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5886">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5886">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5887">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5887">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5888">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5888">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5889">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5889">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5890">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5890">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5891">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5891">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5892">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5892">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5893">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5893">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5894">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5894">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5895">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5895">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5896">Keywords_poland_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5896">Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5899">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5899">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5900">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5900">driver licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5903">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5903">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5904">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5904">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5905">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5905">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5906">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5906">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5907">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5907">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5908">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5908">dlno#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5910">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5910">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5911">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5911">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5912">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5912">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5913">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5913">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5914">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5914">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5915">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5915">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5916">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5916">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5917">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5917">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5918">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5918">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5919">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5919">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5920">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5920">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5921">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5921">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5922">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5922">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5923">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5923">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5924">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5924">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5925">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5925">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5926">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5926">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5927">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5927">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5928">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5928">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5929">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5929">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5930">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5930">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5931">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5931">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5932">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5932">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5933">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5933">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5934">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5934">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5935">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5935">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5936">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5936">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5937">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5937">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5938">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5938">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5939">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5939">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5940">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5940">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5941">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5941">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5942">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5942">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5943">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5943">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5944">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5944">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5945">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5945">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5946">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5946">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5947">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5947">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5948">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5948">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5960">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5960">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5961">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5961">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5962">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5962">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5963">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5963">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5964">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5964">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5965">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5965">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5966">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5966">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5967">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5967">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5968">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5968">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5969">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5969">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5970">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5970">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5971">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5971">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5972">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5972">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5973">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5973">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5975">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5975">Numer paszportu</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5978">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5978">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5979">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5979">Poland REGON number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5980">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5980">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5981">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5981">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5982">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5982">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5983">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5983">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5984">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5984">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5985">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5985">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5986">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5986">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5987">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5987">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5988">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5988">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5989">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5989">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-5990">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5990">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5991">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5991">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5992">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5992">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5993">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5993">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-5994">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5994">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-5995">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-5995">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6012">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6012">Poland tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6013">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6013">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6014">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6014">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6015">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6015">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6016">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6016">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6017">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6017">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6018">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6018">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6019">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6019">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6020">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6020">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6021">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6021">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6022">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6022">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6052">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6052">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6053">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6054">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6054">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6055">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6055">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6056">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6056">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6057">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6057">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6058">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6058">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6059">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6059">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6060">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6060">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6061">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6061">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6062">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6062">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6070">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6070">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6071">Идентификация нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6071">identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6072">identification number
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6072">identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6074">Номер идентификационной карточки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6074">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6075">номер национальной идентификационной карточки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6075">national id card</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6082">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6082">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6083">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6083">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6084">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6084">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6085">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь чисел в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6085">two letters followed by a seven numbers in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6086">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6086">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6087">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6087">two letters followed by seven numbers with special characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6088">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6088">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6089">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6089">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6090">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6090">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6091">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6091">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6092">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6092">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6093">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6093">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6094">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6094">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6095">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6095">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6096">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6096">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6097">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6097">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6098">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6098">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6099">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6099">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6103">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6103">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6104">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6104">driver licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6107">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6107">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6108">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6108">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6109">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6109">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6110">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6110">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6111">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6111">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6114">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6114">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6115">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6115">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6116">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6116">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6117">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6117">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6118">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6118">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6119">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6119">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6120">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6120">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6121">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6121">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6122">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6122">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6123">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6123">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6124">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6124">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6125">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6125">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6126">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6126">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6127">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6127">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6128">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6128">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6129">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6129">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span></span>
