- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6132">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6132">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6133">нúмеро Do пассапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6133">número do passaporte</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6134">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6134">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6135">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6135">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6136">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6136">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6137">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6137">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6138">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6138">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6139">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6139">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6140">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6140">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6141">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6141">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6142">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6142">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6143">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6143">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6144">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6144">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6145">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6145">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6146">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6146">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6147">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6147">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6148">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6148">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6149">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6149">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6150">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6150">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6175">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6175">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6176">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6176">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6178">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6178">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6180">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6180">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6181">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6181">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6182">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6182">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6183">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6183">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6184">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6184">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6185">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6185">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6186">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6186">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6187">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6187">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6188">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6188">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6204">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6204">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6205">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6205">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6206">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6206">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6207">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6207">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6208">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6208">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6209">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6209">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6210">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6210">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6211">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6211">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6212">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6212">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6213">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6213">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6214">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6214">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6215">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6215">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6216">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6216">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6217">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6217">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6218">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6218">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6219">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6219">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6234">national id</span></span>

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6270">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6270">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6271">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6271">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6272">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6272">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6273">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6273">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6274">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6274">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6275">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6275">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6276">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6276">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6277">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6277">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6278">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6278">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6279">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6279">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6280">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6280">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6281">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6281">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6282">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6282">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6283">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6283">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6284">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6284">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6286">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6286">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6288">Номер паспорта для России (Россия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6288">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6289">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6290">номер из десяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6290">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6291">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6292">номер из десяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6292">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6293">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6293">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6294">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6294">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6295">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6295">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6296">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6296">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6297">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6297">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6298">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6298">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6299">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6299">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6300">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6300">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6301">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6301">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6302">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6302">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6303">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6303">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6320">Номер паспорта для России Международная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6320">Russia passport number international</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6321">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6321">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6322">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6322">nine digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6323">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6323">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6324">девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6324">nine digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6325">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6325">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6326">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6326">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6330">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6330">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6331">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6331">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6332">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6332">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6350">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6350">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6351">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6351">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6352">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6352">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6353">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6353">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6354">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6354">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6355">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6355">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6356">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6356">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6357">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6357">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6358">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6358">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6359">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6359">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6360">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6360">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6361">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6361">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6362">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6362">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6363">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6363">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6364">I card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6364">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6365">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6365">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6366">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6366">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6367">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6367">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6368">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6368">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6369">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6369">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6370">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6370">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6371">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6371">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6372">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6372">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6373">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6373">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6374">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6374">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6375">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6375">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6376">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6376">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6377">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6377">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6378">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6378">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6379">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6379">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6380">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6380">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6381">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6381">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6382">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6382">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6383">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6383">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6384">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6384">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6395">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словакия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6395">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6396">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6396">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6397">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6397">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6398">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6398">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6399">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6399">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6400">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6400">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6401">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6401">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6402">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6402">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6403">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6403">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6404">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6404">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6405">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6405">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6406">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6406">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6407">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6407">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6408">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6408">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovaknia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6424">Словакия персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6424">Slovakia personal number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6425">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6425">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6426">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательную обратную косую черту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6426">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6427">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6427">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6428">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6428">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6429">Необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6429">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6430">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6430">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6431">1 обязательная контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6431">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6432">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6433">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6433">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6434">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6435">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6435">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6436">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6436">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6437">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6437">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6438">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6438">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6439">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6439">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6440">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6440">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6441">Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6441">Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6442">азоносíтó сзáм</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6442">azonosító szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6443">номер рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6443">birth number</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6486">Словакия — номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6486">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6487">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6487">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6488">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6488">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6489">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6489">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6490">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6490">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6491">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6491">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6492">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6492">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6493">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6493">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6494">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6494">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6495">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6495">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6496">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6496">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6497">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6497">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6498">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6498">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6499">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6499">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6500">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6500">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6501">номер паспорта словакиан</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6501">slovakian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6502">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6502">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6503">číсло Пасу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6503">číslo pasu</span></span>


## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6504">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6504">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6505">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6505">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6506">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6507">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6507">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6509">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6509">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6510">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6511">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6511">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6512">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6513">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6513">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6514">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6514">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6515">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6515">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6516">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6516">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6517">Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6517">Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6531">Словения уникальный номер хозяина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6531">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6532">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6532">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6533">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6533">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6534">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6534">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6535">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6535">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6536">семь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ДДММЛЛЛ), где "ЛЛЛ" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6536">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6537">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6537">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6538">три цифры, которые соответствуют сочетанию пола и серийного номера для людей, которые приставили один и тот же день (000-499 для пола и 500-999 для розетки)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6538">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6539">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6539">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6540">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6540">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6541">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6541">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6542">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6542">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6543">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6543">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6544">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6544">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6545">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6545">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6546">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6546">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6547">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6547">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

        </Pattern>

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6575">Номер паспорта для Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6575">Slovenia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6576">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6576">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6577">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6578">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6578">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6579">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6580">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6580">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6581">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6581">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6582">одна прописная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6582">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6583">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6583">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6585">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6585">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6587">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6587">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6588">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6588">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6589">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6589">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6590">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6590">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6591">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6591">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6592">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6592">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6593">номер паспорта для словенского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6593">slovenian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6594">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6594">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6595">Список потнега šтевилка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6595">številka potnega lista</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6596">Идентификационный номер для налога на Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6596">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6597">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6597">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6598">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6598">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6599">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6599">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6600">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6600">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6601">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6601">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6602">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6602">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6603">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6603">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6604">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6604">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6605">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6605">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6606">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6606">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6607">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6607">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6608">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6608">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6609">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6609">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6610">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6610">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6634">Идентификационный номер Южно-Африканского Республика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6634">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6635">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6635">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6636">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6636">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6637">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6637">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6638">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6638">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6639">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6639">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6640">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6640">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6641">Индикатор гражданства, состоящих из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6641">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6642">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6642">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6643">одна цифра контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6643">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6644">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6644">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6645">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6645">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6646">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6646">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6647">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6647">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6648">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6648">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6649">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6649">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6650">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6650">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6652">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6652">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6656">Регистрационный номер резидентной Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6656">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6657">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6657">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6658">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6658">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6659">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6659">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6660">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6660">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6661">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6661">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6662">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6662">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6663">одна цифра, определяемая столетием и пол</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6663">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6664">код региона рождения из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6664">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6665">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6665">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6666">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6666">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6668">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6668">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6670">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6670">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6671">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6671">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6672">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6672">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6673">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6673">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6674">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6674">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6675">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6675">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6676">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6676">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6677">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6677">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6678">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6678">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6679">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6679">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6680">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6680">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6681">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6681">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6682">ррн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6682">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6683">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6683">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6684">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6684">Spain driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6685">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6685">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6686">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6686">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6687">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6687">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6688">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6688">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6689">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6689">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6690">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6690">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6691">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6691">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6692">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6693">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6693">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6694">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6695">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6695">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6696">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6696">The function  `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6697">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6697">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6734">Испания, DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6734">Spain DNI</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6735">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6736">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6736">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6737">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6738">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6738">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6739">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6739">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6740">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6740">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6741">один проверочный символ (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6741">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6742">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6742">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6743">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6743">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6744">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6744">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6745">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6745">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6746">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6746">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6747">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6747">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6748">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6748">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6749">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6749">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6773">Номер паспорта для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6773">Spain passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6774">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6774">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6775">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6775">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6776">сочетание букв и цифр из восьми или девяти символов без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6776">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6777">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6777">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6778">сочетание букв и цифр из восьми или девяти символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6778">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6779">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6779">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6780">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6780">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6781">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6781">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6782">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6782">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6783">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6783">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6784">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6784">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3def0-6785">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6785">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6786">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6786">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6787">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6787">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="3def0-6788">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6788">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6792">Книга Passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6792">passport book</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3def0-6793">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3def0-6793">passport number</span></span>
